<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
    <title>Template Purchase Successful</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
      .header { background-color: #14a800; padding: 24px; text-align: center; }
      .header h1 { color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
      .body { padding: 32px; }
      .body p { color: #444444; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; }
      .success-box { background-color: #f0faf0; border-left: 4px solid #14a800; border-radius: 4px; padding: 16px; margin: 24px 0; }
      .success-box p { margin: 4px 0; color: #276749; font-size: 14px; }
      .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #14a800; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 15px; margin: 16px 0; }
      .footer { background-color: #f4f4f4; text-align: center; padding: 16px; color: #aaaaaa; font-size: 12px; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>GeniusBid</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="body">
        <p>Hi <strong><%= name %></strong>,</p>
        <p>Your template purchase was successful. You now have full access to the template below.</p>
        <div class="success-box">
          <p><strong>Template:</strong> <%= templateTitle %></p>
          <p><strong>Category:</strong> <%= category %></p>
          <p><strong>Amount Paid:</strong> $<%= amountPaid %></p>
        </div>
        <p>You can access your purchased templates anytime from your library.</p>
        <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>/templates/library" class="button">View My Library</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= year %> GeniusBid. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>